thread.title: Helga

author: Helga
title: Helga
text: I'm an exchange student here in Australia and I came her on Friday and moved in on Sunday the week after. It is very easy to find an accommodation through Flatmate. I really recommend to not trust the photos and visit the place before you rent it! But I would have started looking in my home country and arrange inspect right away when I arrived here. But I was very lucky and found an apartment in very short time.
